section.div: Just a guy making random things! Can often be found coding with a toaster, while my dog stares confusedly.
I don't really have a goal, but it's great to have one to work towards! (My main goal is to make people happy!)

div.p: I love to work on Open-Source projects, as well as help people make stuff! Feel free to contact me on Discord if neccessary, or E-Mail! Discord: fayevr
